      ],
      "lines": [
        "答案是 <term id=\"graph_embedding\">图嵌入</term> 框架。",
        "它把降维问题归结为图的构建和优化。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s053",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "首先构建一个 <term id=\"intrinsic_graph\">内在图</term>。",
        "图中的边表示我们希望保持的相似关系。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s054",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "再构建一个 <term id=\"penalty_graph\">惩罚图</term>。",
        "图中的边表示我们希望拉远的关系。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "laplacian_matrix"
      ],
      "id": "s055",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "laplacian_matrix"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "然后定义 <term id=\"laplacian_matrix\">拉普拉斯矩阵</term>。",
        "\\(L = D - S\\)，其中 \\(D\\) 是度矩阵。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "y^{*} = \\arg\\min_{y^T y = 1 \\text{ or } y^T B y = 1} y^T L y",
        "spoken": "最小化拉普拉斯二次型，同时满足归一化约束"
      },
      "id": "s056",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "降维的目标是：在低维空间中保持内在图的相似性。"
      ],
      "type": "formula"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s057",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "不同的降维方法，只是内在图和惩罚图定义不同。",
        "PCA、LDA、LLE、Isomap 都可以纳入这个框架。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "exercise": {
        "answer": 1,
        "explanation": "不同方法只是内在图和惩罚图的定义不同，优化框架是统一的。",
